::KitKat::
She watched at Bloodystrike flew off. "Well, so much for them." she 
wondered what was the matter. He flew off without any formalities. 
She shrugged and didn't worry about it.  She kept walking to the 
base.  She knew she would shortly arrive there.

> "Let's go!"
>
